        "content": "<p>Hi everyone!</p>\n<p>I am implementing a new formal language called Litex — a simple formal language designed to make mathematical formalization accessible to everyone, even 10-year-old beginners! <span aria-label=\"rocket\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f680\" role=\"img\" title=\"rocket\">:rocket:</span> With 3000+ GitHub commits and growing, Litex is now capable of handling real mathematical examples. My name is Jiachen Shen, and as a passionate language design geek, I've created Litex to bridge the gap between abstract formal systems and human intuition.</p>\n<p>This week I implemented basic features to formalize √2 ∉ ℚ and ℝ, Z ∈ Group in Litex. Visit <a href=\"https://litexlang.org/playground\">https://litexlang.org/playground</a> to try the following examples. Visit my Github <a href=\"https://github.com/litexlang/golitex\">https://github.com/litexlang/golitex</a> (star this repo <span aria-label=\"star\" class=\"emoji emoji-2b50\" role=\"img\" title=\"star\">:star:</span> !) for more detailed introduction to Litex. Join our zulip <a href=\"https://litex.zulipchat.com/join/c4e7foogy6paz2sghjnbujov/\">https://litex.zulipchat.com/join/c4e7foogy6paz2sghjnbujov/</a> for discussions. The email is <a href=\"mailto:litexlang@outlook.com\">litexlang@outlook.com</a>. </p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/5Firp4tJ_fqu2xQTjG1LOg2K/sqrt2_is_irrational.png\">sqrt2_is_irrational.png</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/hkS0OMOiRhXJ7OFs2JOOsgFq/z_r_are_groups.png\">z_r_are_groups.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/5Firp4tJ_fqu2xQTjG1LOg2K/sqrt2_is_irrational.png\" title=\"sqrt2_is_irrational.png\"><img data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"1320x1274\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/5Firp4tJ_fqu2xQTjG1LOg2K/sqrt2_is_irrational.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/hkS0OMOiRhXJ7OFs2JOOsgFq/z_r_are_groups.png\" title=\"z_r_are_groups.png\"><img data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"1418x816\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/hkS0OMOiRhXJ7OFs2JOOsgFq/z_r_are_groups.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
