        "content": "<p>He don't even know how to write a correct capture-avoiding substitution.<span aria-label=\"rolling on the floor laughing\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f923\" role=\"img\" title=\"rolling on the floor laughing\">:rolling_on_the_floor_laughing:</span><span aria-label=\"point right\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f449\" role=\"img\" title=\"point right\">:point_right:</span></p>",
